{"tid":2262230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周顯:  現在去英國是自尋死路","createTime":"2020-10-29T02:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T02:14:41.000Z","uid":187876,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6ae2c286f15a1310f9db34bd2a457a5b88748c","tid":2262230,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"有朋友夫婦都當教師，有兩個子女，即將移民到英國去了。我心想，英國現時日日兩萬宗新增新冠肺炎個案，日日死百幾人，總人口的1.3%受到感染，還處於高峰期，你此去，不是自尋死路嗎？至少也等到疫情過後，才過去呀！<br />\n<br />\n他也有苦衷，就是要趕上子女的入學期。至於為何10月及11月時會有入學期問題，我沒去深究。<br />\n<br />\n英國近年的經濟，實在「油麻地」，以股市作說明：過去5年，港股不上不下，也算升了7%，英國股市則反跌了7%，這還不算貨幣貶值。<br />\n<br />\n除了2016年英國脫歐，更根本的原因，是在2009年以後，整個歐洲全部都沒好過。我在本欄已說過很多次：美國在金融海嘯後，國力大弱，已從giver變成taker，因此美國迅速復元，歐洲日本卻永不翻身。包括台灣在內很多人看歷史，在二戰之後，所有美國的跟班都發達，以為這一次也不例外，死跟著美國，但形勢已在2009年扭轉了，現在美國附庸只會被進一步剝削，再佔不到便宜了。<br />\n<br />\n英國作為美國的第一號附庸，前途有限，後患無窮，不在話下。現時英國有6,798萬人，其中300萬左右穆斯林，300萬左右黑人，未算其他少數族裔。<br />\n<br />\n由於少數族裔的生育率是白人的15倍，估計到了2050年，他們將佔人口的1/3至一半。也因他們大部分都是住在倫敦，到時倫敦的少數族裔應佔人口的大多數，而且這些人大多是社會的低下階層，這肯定會造成嚴重的社會問題。我實在很為移民英國的朋友的兩個小朋友擔心。<br />\n<br />\n《香港討論區》有人說：「我兩個小朋友在英國讀大學&hellip;&hellip;嗰邊種族歧視十分嚴重，人工低，薪俸稅重，租金高，日用品貴，交通費高昂，膳食冇平嘅，唔帶埋錢過去只靠工作，若要租樓基本上不能生存&hellip;&hellip;一次過交幾年保費，扒手又多&hellip;&hellip;50歲夫婦帶子女去英國移民，基本上需要帶二代人一生所需的金錢&hellip;&hellip;一家幾口就從此成為不用工作的廢人&hellip;&hellip;有前途的工作是不會請黃種人的。他們大學畢業後可以做下樓面，超市執貨，Uber司機，清潔，通渠之類。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%e7%8f%be%e5%9c%a8%e5%8e%bb%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e6%98%af%e8%87%aa%e5%b0%8b%e6%ad%bb%e8%b7%af-240784?fbclid=IwAR22M4y4Vhro_kvQau6d6edF-wY5vjLgOWQHWU7tcMscUmj6C0yL8ZeBV88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%259c%25a8%25e5%258e%25bb%25e8%258b%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2598%25af%25e8%2587%25aa%25e5%25b0%258b%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e8%25b7%25af-240784%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22M4y4Vhro_kvQau6d6edF-wY5vjLgOWQHWU7tcMscUmj6C0yL8ZeBV88&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=8dfbf36e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%e7%8f%be%e5%9c%a8%e5%8e%bb%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e6%98%af%e8%87%aa%e5%b0%8b%e6%ad%bb%e8%b7%af-240784?fbclid=IwAR22M4y4Vhro_kvQau6d6edF-wY5vjLgOWQHWU7tcMscUmj6C0yL8ZeBV88</a>"},{"pid":"fd221be404629076056d3bdc3735b2b84194bf6b","tid":2262230,"uid":299514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾文，拉"},{"pid":"432e7df89e6b35e65c3a5ba7d05f08eee9b62a91","tid":2262230,"uid":30982,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"香討果篇野 你係講緊香港？ 日用品貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c59ec44679baecf2022429d8edd55901ef6548c","tid":2262230,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老藍絲做廢工係正常喎<br />\n<br />\n狗眼不嬲都看人低"},{"pid":"2fc4aabaf7065ea222aa24f3012af8ead2dcd370","tid":2262230,"uid":309989,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:10:48.000Z","msg":"一句講晒，點衰都衰唔過大陸共產黨，on9文"},{"pid":"9c334c58e6095bda274271fb09988d685c0ef651","tid":2262230,"uid":258948,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"遲啲香港都係咁<br />\n支那人做上流工種<br />\n香港人就係做deliveroo<br />\n依家已經開始緊啦傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df7c8f09c91f59097c427df86c3df3a100e2e09","tid":2262230,"uid":53922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"藍絲叫起留係香港供樓都正常既。<br />\nAM730 就咪撚貼link 喇"},{"pid":"695c3ad50415b242ce3b083a4baa069cbb544039","tid":2262230,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁移民去大灣區好唔好?每月3千月薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5b804dbd0b967aae3412f5c15d22361b59843c","tid":2262230,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"一次得罪伊斯蘭教同黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93845ddc87b716b09ac81f32b6641a7b08b70ca1","tid":2262230,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3075686398ded484da0613dd8f3d2fd05527fc81","tid":2262230,"uid":125017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"留香港又係死<br />\n去英國又係死<br />\n世界咁大 點解唔去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07f715f0eabd3c6d075dfe0d8e2318372cb14c6","tid":2262230,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3075686398ded484da0613dd8f3d2fd05527fc81","tid":2262230,"uid":125017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"留香港又係死<br />\n去英國又係死<br />\n世界咁大 點解唔去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"周顯個廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b91b1056376c1641fc075dfa44d4641ea18a2ed","tid":2262230,"uid":33370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"周觀微呢條蛋散就由佢鳩噏啦<br />\n<br />\n條撚屌日日都係鳩噏當秘笈，成日吹到自己政治預測好把炮<br />\n實則係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<strong>我對未來幾年政局的預測</strong><br />\n2020-05-26<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>有人問過我，幾個月後，《國家安全法》正式實施，將會有多少人落網呢？我的答案是：一個人也不會拉，同澳門一樣。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n此話怎說呢？我的看法是：早在法律通過和實施之前，香港政府必然已將所有可以拉的人的拉光了，而且利用港英政府遺留下來的法律，把所有犯事的人都控告了，甚至是所有應該DQ的議員，都DQ了，根本沒有參選的機會。到了這時，根本已經不存在任何可拉的人了。<br />\n<br />\n這做法有甚麼奧義呢？答案是：如果《國家安全法》根本沒有被拉的人，這證明了這法例根本不可怕，也證明了國家的寬大為懷，而之前反對23條的人，都被證明是錯誤了，是杞人憂天了。<br />\n<br />\n然後，下一步，就是修改《基本法》，把所有的法律漏洞都封得死死的，估計中央政府應有否決提名權，以至是把行政長官，以及所有高級官員的任命權，以及罷免權，把整個香港特區政府牢牢的掌握在手裏。<br />\n<br />\n到了這時，大家已經差不多絕望了，政改五部曲就會重啟，行政長官以及所有立法會議員將會全部普選產生，兌現了《基本法》全面普選的承諾，這時，反對派已完蛋了，提名權、任命權、罷免權也在中央的手裡，有乜所謂呢？  </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%BE%E5%B9%B4%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC-220242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%25B8%25AC-220242&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=e4ee5f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%BE%E5%B9%B4%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC-220242</a>"},{"pid":"bfdf1f2939a706bf731f91d13e3ebc6ce6aa6a4d","tid":2262230,"uid":312114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"鳩蜆 仲要quote香討 笑撚左"},{"pid":"eebae6fed8a4bf0575702fed6dfc30c0f4486e68","tid":2262230,"uid":365618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3075686398ded484da0613dd8f3d2fd05527fc81","tid":2262230,"uid":125017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"留香港又係死<br />\n去英國又係死<br />\n世界咁大 點解唔去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<br />\n假設去英國又係死嘅話，我寧願喺英國死，起碼眼光唔淨係停留喺香港"},{"pid":"c67fb049fb454ccf24eb6618be521ff0164f39db","tid":2262230,"uid":275225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"香港都越嚟越多低賤支那<br />\n繁殖能力都勁過本土香港人好多<br />\n而且9成係低下皆層<br />\n樓價又高，經濟準備仆街加永不反身"},{"pid":"96617718417b7594076c62f9bec9c8e754c9c23a","tid":2262230,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebae6fed8a4bf0575702fed6dfc30c0f4486e68","tid":2262230,"uid":365618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3075686398ded484da0613dd8f3d2fd05527fc81","tid":2262230,"uid":125017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"留香港又係死<br />\n去英國又係死<br />\n世界咁大 點解唔去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<br />\n假設去英國又係死嘅話，我寧願喺英國死，起碼眼光唔淨係停留喺香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"留香港係生不如死呀"},{"pid":"c57c8cb70394c379b553485a5f0a206084fce7ef","tid":2262230,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"名校爆退學潮 女拔罕有招插班生 英華書院：全港學校幾有同樣問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2268562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2268562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n事實都擺在眼前"}]}